Millénaire is created by Kinniken and contributors — https://millenaire.org.
The original mod's source has historically been made available by its author,
but WITHOUT a formal open-source licence; all rights to it are reserved by its
author. Therefore:

  * This repository does NOT contain and does NOT redistribute Millénaire's
