  * The 26.2-format resource definitions we authored to drive that code:
    blockstates, block/item models, item-model definitions, loot tables,
    recipes, advancements (src/main/resources), and the small number of
    textures we created ourselves.
  * The build tooling, the upstream-fetch script, and documentation.

